  "general_provisions": "This resolution encourages the State Board of Education and local education agencies to create and offer instruction in courses that will prepare students for certain careers.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>acknowledges the importance of specialized technical skills and industry-recognized credentials for a skilled workforce and improved economic strength;<hr><ltbullet>supports efforts to improve technical education; and<hr><ltbullet>encourages the State Board of Education and local education agencies to:<hr><ltbullet1>expand instruction related to technical education;<hr><ltbullet1>collaborate with certain partners; and<hr><ltbullet1>use certain existing programs.",
